description:
Have you ever wanted to hear a completely random number? Well, your wait is over! Our Randomizer Skill enables you to simply ask for any random number whenever you want!

Beyond that, we enable you to ask for numbers greater than or less than other numbers! All you have to do is preface your question with the phrase
“Alexa, ask Randomizer”. With our skill, there are infinite opportunities for fun, literally!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Randomizer for a random number.
Alexa, ask Randomizer for any number greater than fifty.
Alexa, ask Randomizer for any random number less than ten.
name: Randomizer
shortDescription: Use the Randomizer skill for all of your Random Number Needs!  Simply ask Alexa!
